				<td><font face="verdana" size="1">
				<img src="http://www.everlore.com/gimages/open.gif">&nbsp;<a href="/quests/default.asp">Quests</a><br>
				<img src="http://www.everlore.com/gimages/tline.gif">
				<img src="http://www.everlore.com/gimages/open.gif">&nbsp;<a href="default.asp?land=1283">South Karana</a><br>
				<img src="http://www.everlore.com/gimages/tline3.gif">
				<img src="http://www.everlore.com/gimages/open.gif">&nbsp;<b>Bard at the Fountain</b><br><br>
				</td>
			</tr>
				
			<tr>
			<td>
				<p>
					<font face="verdana" size="3"><b>    Bard at the Fountain</b>&nbsp;<a href="../Subscribe.asp?DID=1680"><font face="Verdana" size="2">[Subscribe to this document]</font></a></font>
					<br>
					<font face="verdana" size="2">
					<b><a href="mailto:nuttah@psn.net">Gizzard the Wizzard</a> | 
		                        12/28/1999 3:13:45 PM</b></font></p>
					
					<p>
					<font face="verdana" size="2">If you speak to the Bard near the fountain in South Karana, he will ask you if you want to hear a song. If you listen to this song he will ask you if you think it is a happy or sad song. I said sad and he then told me that he had something stolen from him by a hermit. There is a hermit in the SE part of the zone in a walled compound, however the building he is in is locked and I have not been able to progress any further.<BR>
<BR>
If anyone knows how to finish please post on this site.<BR>
<BR>
Giz
			<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</font></p>
					</p>
			</td>
			</tr>
