				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				Played with the Hermit last night, leveled to 20th too.<BR>
<BR>
For Bard's<BR>
<BR>
19th he con's Yellow<BR>
Drops rare Fine Steel Weapons<BR>
Cash : usually around 1gp in small coins, but sometimes he drops 1pp and some smaller denominations.<BR>
<BR>
To get him out of the house, stand at the back of the house with the chimney on your left and snuggle into the corner.  Say 'I will fight you', he will say 'So B It Fool'. and will probably get a melee on you before you get back from the house.<BR>
<BR>
He has 2 main casts, Skin of Thorns and a blast which does moderate damage.<BR>
<BR>
He drops - Cracked Flute (non-playable) and the first song sheet for this quest.<BR>
<BR>
Overall a great place to level as I found out!
