				Yes, AE spells will work. What a cleric friend of mine would do is immediately after killing him, we would get in position for him again, and rest.. He would be right by the hermits house against the wall. (right in the back by the chimney facing the door) As soon as we saw &quot;a hermit casts a spell&quot; He let loose with the AE spell, and that would draw the hermit out. Also, another tried way, and it DOES work, hehe...if you are a DE Necro... just walk up to the back of the house. Trust me, he will come out of there quick, looking to do you a tad of harm.... And the he does drop FS weapons, but from what I saw, only about 10-15% of the the time. He also occasionally has words on him, so good luck!
